snippet.title: The Sims 4 Dine Out: Own Restaurants Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In The Sims 4 Dine Out, build your restaurant, become the owner, and run it your way!
 
Learn how to customize your restaurants: http://x.ea.com/5254
 
You are in control of owning and running a restaurant. Hire and outfit staff, set the menu and prices, and chat up diners to improve customer satisfaction. Strive for a five-star rating or build a multi-restaurant empire to rake in the Simoleons!
